            "id": "4580250",
            "title": "The Joint to sell 45 clinics for $2.3M; shifts to franchise-only model",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li data-end=\"140\" data-start=\"0\">The Joint (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JYNT\" title=\"The Joint Corp.\">JYNT</a></span>) announced on Monday that it will sell 45 company-run clinics in Southern California to Elite Chiro Group for about $2.3M.</li>\n<li data-end=\"315\" data-start=\"142\">Out of these, Elite Chiro Group has already taken over daily operations of 32 clinics from April 27, 2026, under a temporary management deal until full ownership transfer.</li>\n<li data-end=\"426\" data-start=\"317\">The remaining 13 clinics will also be fully handed over once lease and ownership formalities are completed.</li>\n<li data-end=\"611\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-start=\"428\">After this deal and two other pending sales, The Joint (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/JYNT\" title=\"The Joint Corp.\">JYNT</a>) will be left with just 3 company-managed clinics out of a total of 960 locations, moving closer to a franchise-only model.</li>\n<li data-end=\"611\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-start=\"428\">Source: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20489090-the-joint-corp-signs-asset-purchase-agreement-to-sell-45-corporate-owned-clinics-in-southern\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Press Release\">Press Release</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
