            "id": "4580220",
            "title": "SA analyst: AI stocks lift market despite oil and yield pressures",
            "description": "<html><body><p data-eci=\"true\">Wall Street’s muted start to the week masked a market being pulled in competing directions, as investors positioned themselves for a heavy slate of catalysts.</p>\n<p>“Investors continue to chase the AI capex beneficiaries… This is keeping the overall sentiment positive, despite the rising oil prices and rising 10Y yields,” noted Seeking Alpha analyst <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/damir-tokic\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Damir Tokic\">Damir Tokic</a>, underscoring the tension between optimism and emerging risks.</p>\n<p>That dynamic was reflected in Monday’s price action as the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SP500</a>) edged up +0.1%, while the Nasdaq Composite (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COMP:IND\" title=\"NASDAQ Composite Index\">COMP:IND</a></span></span>) also gained +0.1% on the trading day and the Dow Jones Industrial Average (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DJI\" title=\"Dow Jones Industrial Average Index\">DJI</a></span></span>) ended lower by -0.1%.</p>\n<p>Tokic pointed to companies tied to AI infrastructure—particularly memory, storage, and chipmakers—as key drivers of sentiment, with standout momentum in firms like Micron (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MU\" title=\"Micron Technology, Inc.\">MU</a>), SanDisk (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SNDK\" title=\"Sandisk Corporation\">SNDK</a>), and Nvidia (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NVDA\" title=\"NVIDIA Corporation\">NVDA</a>) pushing markets toward record levels. </p>\n<p>However, Tokic warned that rising oil prices and climbing Treasury yields are beginning to signal inflationary pressures tied to the evolving U.S.-Iran conflict.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, the analyst went on to say: “The VIX index remains just below 20 in advance of the Fed meeting and key tech earnings, both of which could boost volatility this week.” </p>\n<p><strong>Market Tracking ETFs:</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DIA\" title=\"State Street SPDR Dow Jones Indust Avg ETF Trust\">DIA</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DDM\" title=\"ProShares Ultra Dow30 ETF\">DDM</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DOG\" title=\"ProShares Short Dow30 ETF\">DOG</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DXD\" title=\"ProShares UltraShort Dow30 ETF\">DXD</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SDOW\" title=\"ProShares UltraPro Short Dow30 ETF\">SDOW</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"State Street SPDR S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VOO\" title=\"Vanguard 500 Index Fund ETF\">VOO</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IVV\" title=\"iShares Core S&amp;P 500 ETF\">IVV</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RSP\" title=\"Invesco S&amp;P 500 Eql Wght ETF\">RSP</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SSO\" title=\"ProShares Ultra S&amp;P500 ETF\">SSO</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UPRO\" title=\"ProShares UltraPro S&amp;P500 ETF\">UPRO</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SH\" title=\"ProShares Short S&amp;P500 ETF\">SH</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SDS\" title=\"ProShares UltraShort S&amp;P500 ETF\">SDS</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPXU\" title=\"ProShares UltraPro Short S&amp;P500 ETF\">SPXU</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QQQ\" title=\"Invesco QQQ Trust, Series 1 ETF\">QQQ</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QQQM\" title=\"Invesco NASDAQ 100 ETF\">QQQM</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TQQQ\" title=\"ProShares UltraPro QQQ ETF\">TQQQ</a></span></span>), (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/QID\" title=\"ProShares UltraShort QQQ ETF\">QID</a></span></span>), and (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SQQQ\" title=\"ProShares UltraPro Short QQQ ETF\">SQQQ</a></span></span>).</p>\n<div class=\"signup_widget_placeholder\"></div>\n</body></html>",
